std_msgs/Header header
float64 x          # Global X position (m)
float64 y          # Global Y position (m)
float64 theta      # Heading angle (rad)
float64 vx         # Linear velocity X (m/s)
float64 vy         # Linear velocity Y (m/s)
float64 omega      # Angular velocity (rad/s)
float64 speed      # Scalar speed (m/s)
float64 steering_angle  # Front wheel steering angle (rad)
